
Kasaragod Fish Curry: Tangy fish curry made with coconut and tamarind.
Neypathiri: Deep-fried rice flour bread, often paired with curries.
Kallummakkaya Ularthiyathu: Mussels cooked with shallots, spices, and coconut slices.
Kanji Payar: Rice porridge served with green gram curry.
Thalassery Biriyani: A fragrant rice dish cooked with chicken or mutton.